{
  "stem": "1363.4",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And we brought in new habits, eating habits, schnitzel, spaghetti bolognese, coffee, a-- interior decoration.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We had different tastes for-- of the Australian, Anglo-Saxon.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And we were knocked about it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We were knocked about how we spoke, because we couldn't speak Australian English.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Some of the Hungarians spoke English English.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And, eventually, we picked up, through work and through learning, and this, that, and the other.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I tell you what, I got very tough.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I got very tough.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I became a man.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Through rescuing my auntie, with whom I was-- very often had to help her in those five days, and carry her, so to say, from the sleeping place to a cot.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And, somehow, the responsibility was always on my shoulder after, either with her or with my brother.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And when my brother wasn't then the responsibility-- because my two husbands weren't really money-spinners, and we just, as immigrants, couldn't make a living of one salary.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So, we-- I always had to egg him on to work a bit harder, that we get somewhere.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And the same with, with the children.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "It's-- I always had-- I always had the burden on my shoulder that I have to be the leader.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I'll never forget that my-- the father of my children always said, when there's a big thing, he has to decide.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "When there are small things, I decide.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And in our marriage, never anything big happens.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "So, he took it in a-- in a humorous way.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "But I always had the burden that I have to look after certain people who weren't strong enough.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And even among friends.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I have a girlfriend who lost her husband, and she's very, very vulnerable and weak.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
